|price      = 2000
|location   = Lavander Town
}}

The '''Lucky Incense''' is a type of battle item. It temporarily boosts the player's money gained by 50% for 30 seconds.


==Details==
===Description===
+50% Bonus to money gained

===Acquisition===
{{ItemPrice/head‎|Battle items}}
{{ItemPrice|Dungeon Drop|Random}}
{{ItemPrice|Lavander Town|{{pdollar}}2000}}
|}
|}


== Trivia ==
* This Lucky Incense shares its name, design and function with the official Lucky Incense from the Pokemon franchise. 


